replies.body:
I really like me in Norway, but I want to try to live in the UK somewhere for a year or so. I am actually considering moving to an other countr and go one year on school there (have to get a bit older though). 

Without schoolwork and training I spend a lot time on avicus, reading books, and netflix. 

As a person: You are nice to me, and I really appreciate it! When someone do something you dont like at all to you you complain about it all the time, cut it out please :c.
As a player: You are a good pvper when you try, and you communicate well. You don't seem to get salty, and always remember us to write gg which is a good thing =p
As a leader: I like your strating. Sometimes you make weird choices with the sub in-out but I know that's up to you.

Fav music is anything really. I like to study to clasic music like Mozart though.
